DSPy-compiled prompt cache. Layout:

  compiled-prompts/
    <task-name>/
      <normalised-model>.json

e.g.

  compiled-prompts/
    extract_lease_terms/
      claude-haiku-4-5.json
      claude-sonnet-4-6.json
      gpt-5.json

CompiledPrompts are produced at deploy time by `compileSignature()`
against a target model and stored here. Runtime loads via `PromptCache`.

Re-compile when:
  - the Signature's versionHash changes (Signature.inputs/outputs/objective edit)
  - the routed model changes (new file under <task>/)
  - Inspect harness flags a regression (caller deletes the stale file)
